TEMPORARY EDITOR DOCUMENTATION
--------------------------------------------

START THE EDITOR

  $ ./phear -e <map>

USE THE EDITOR

  Keys 0-9 places objects, 's' saves the map, 'q' quits,
  'l' enables lock-mode (lets you draw using the arrow-keys)

PLAY YOUR MAP

  $ ./phear <map>

SEND IT IN!

  Please send your maps to tom@x86.no. A web based archive
  of custom maps will be made available if there is any
  interest for such a thing..
